# 📝 Materials and Methods Generator

This tool generates a draft "Materials and Methods" text block aligned with the **QUAREP-LiMi minimal reporting requirements** for light microscopy ([Better reporting is better science](https://rupress.org/jcb/article/225/3/e202601032/281525/Better-reporting-is-better-science-Community)). Select a system, choose the specific hardware you used, and click **"Add to Methods"**. You can repeat this process for multiple microscopes and then complete any placeholders with experiment-specific metadata before publication.
